{"tid":1569474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[呼籲] 黑旗海 黑旗海 十一全民黑旗 賀佢老母","createTime":"2019-09-14T15:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T07:30:14.000Z","uid":275386,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7e68cfaf448a1764fe5674ce08a42d72e24eba34","tid":1569474,"uid":275386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:39:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>十一出街 全民黑旗</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n紫荊黑旗、口號黑旗、chinazi 黑旗、自我創作黑旗、乜撚嘢黑旗都好，10月1號出嚟行街嘅都全部攞住支黑旗賀佢老母！<br />\n<br />\n有錢嘅就搵人大批量製作，冇銀両嘅就自家小手作用心思去做，大大細細乜撚嘢size 都唔拘，黑底反白，最緊要夠多，全民黑旗海，同佢老母做忌！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港    時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f90f225d031dddda3407e9d40b92e6cf454b6d57","tid":1569474,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:46:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span> <br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"f25cd5a1caed7d9f1bad0fb11178afb9a2d6bbf1","tid":1569474,"uid":275386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:50:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2fc0f84d01d2f1df395ec6be7167b140889292e","tid":1569474,"uid":275386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:50:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6cfa806a5b8f0f3259661614a0daab2fd132f8cd","tid":1569474,"uid":275386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:50:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b99f352e43db2764361747307e729f8d12aac806","tid":1569474,"uid":275386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:50:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"661d28c3e9d6e91318d0198bbb0396f112bd6438","tid":1569474,"uid":275386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:50:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bdce16536fb1cd715092fcedd6156e0c5a4f7392","tid":1569474,"uid":275386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s